WINDOW DRIVE就淨係裝WINDOW好似會無咁似出事<br />\n你最好記底有咩APPS之後裝番"},{"pid":"f242b902c99fab14631d878ab40ed1fd3c3b1806","tid":485242,"uid":76940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我入過一次<br />\n有重新裝win10<br />\n我唔太記得   好似係選左保留資料/檔案咁樣重裝<br />\n你可以查清楚d先</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試過 都唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好保留資料重裝<br />\n將D 唔係SYSTEM既野放番落個HDD度<br />\n個WINDOW DRIVE就淨係裝WINDOW好似會無咁似出事<br />\n你最好記底有咩APPS之後裝番</blockquote><br />\n好 唔該曬 我聽日試試佢"},{"pid":"7b99d04b7e7da8d73b69cd2fcd61c08d4ed8c7a0","tid":485242,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我入過一次<br />\n有重新裝win10<br />\n我唔太記得   好似係選左保留資料/檔案咁樣重裝<br />\n你可以查清楚d先</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試過 都唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好保留資料重裝<br />\n將D 唔係SYSTEM既野放番落個HDD度<br />\n個WINDOW DRIVE就淨係裝WINDOW好似會無咁似出事<br />\n你最好記底有咩APPS之後裝番</blockquote><br />\n好 唔該曬 我聽日試試佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢叫你簡邊個DRIVE裝個時最好 格式化左同刪左啲分區"},{"pid":"6b409ab1f14ce0b3428835be9b0a1ed10fcdbb43","tid":485242,"uid":136287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識電腦嘅人就咩都賴windows先<br />\n<br />\n你覺得windows會唔開機一排再開返就用唔到咩 擺明用家問題啦 好意思話垃圾win10</blockquote><br />\n十分認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf3fec39dbcff389dd7886a8d5fba5d0c3d4532","tid":485242,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"炒咗重裝"},{"pid":"67b828eb42ce81c9e311d1431e54fde030109e81","tid":485242,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"重裝啦柒頭"},{"pid":"2beba2653bf670908eeb2435dcff0e6a09840391","tid":485242,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"之前部HP試過, 自動修復唔得, 仲有個CHECK POINT restore返就入得返去, 不過唔太記得係點禁, 網上有教"},{"pid":"b1397117d452ad9cc3586